Second Application for Epam training. Traffic Light. Console application.
This program simulates work of  traffic light.
For start the program in the console, you should input number and press enter, after that program show you,
what color caught fire on traffic light.
For start application in IDE IntelliJ Idea press Shift+F10 or click on green triangle.
For stop press Shift+F10 or click on red square.
The program contains three classes. 
Class Lights which des—Åribing kinds of lights of traffic light. 
Class TrafficLightMethods which gives methods for working with entered values.
Class Main which start the program.

